<main class="container mx-auto my-[11%] px-[5%]">
  <div
    class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row bg-white rounded-[8px] shadow-xl mx-auto overflow-hidden"
  >
    <div
      class="w-full lg:w-1/3 flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-8 px-5"
      style="background-image: url('/images/cover.png')"
    >
      <h2 class="text-white text-[22px] font-bold">充值驗證頁面</h2>
      <span class="text-white text-[12px] opacity-70"
        >這是一個獨立的,加密頁面,您必須驗證賬號有效性!</span
      >
    </div>
    <div class="w-full lg:w-2/3 py-10 px-10">
      <form action="/premium/check-user-key" method="POST">
        <h2 class="font-bold mt-5">&#10148; Connect Key:</h2>
        <div class="mt-1">
          <input
            class="w-full border rounded-[4px] border-gray-500 py-1 px-2"
            value="<%=conn_key%>"
            name="conn_key"
            id="conn_key"
            type="text"
            required
          />
          <span class="text-xs text-red-700"
            >*&nbsp;不要在任何公共網絡展示這個私人頁面,不要將 connect key 與你的
            email 同時展示在公共網路!</span
          ><br />
          <span class="text-xs text-red-700"
            >*&nbsp;connect key 是一個私人,且動態變更的公鑰,您無需記憶!</span
          >
        </div>

        <h2 class="font-bold mt-5">&#10148; You'r Email:</h2>
        <div class="mt-1">
          <input
            class="w-full border rounded-[4px] border-gray-500 py-1 px-2"
            name="email"
            id="email"
            type="email"
            placeholder="* Email..."
            required
          />
          <span class="text-xs text-red-700">*&nbsp;請填寫您的郵箱賬號</span>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-5">
          <button
            class="w-full border rounded-[4px] bg-purple-500 py-2 text-white"
            type="submit"
          >
            提交驗證
          </button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
<%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>
